<template>
  <TableView :headers="tableHeaders" :body="tableBody" />
</template>

<script>
import TableView from "@/components/Table/TableView.vue";
import http from '@/services/http.js';

export default {
  components: {
    TableView
  },
  data() {
    return {
      tableHeaders: ['Nome Lotérica', 'Tipo Diagnóstico', 'Data de Criação', 'Valores'],
      tableBody: [
        ['Apple MacBook Pro 17"', 'Silver', 'Laptop', '$2999'],
        ['Microsoft Surface Pro', 'White', 'Laptop PC', '$1999'],
        ['Magic Mouse 2', 'Black', 'Accessories', '$99']
      ]
    };
  },
  methods: {
    async getResults() {
      try {
        const response = await http.get('/results');
        console.log(response.data);
        // Atualize o tableBody com os dados recebidos
        this.tableBody = response.data;
      } catch (error) {
        console.log(error.response);
      }
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.getResults();
  }
};
</script>
